title: Hawkwind 1972 Berlin (Silver Machine,Welcome) -FLAC
description:
Quality: 8

A very early (May 1972) rendition of Silver Machine, in the style of the Roundhouse recording 3 months earlier that appeared on the Glastonbury Fayre album, Calvert on vocals. That recording metamorphosed into the hit single with Lemmy on vocals, and this recording didn&#039;t!

I think it&#039;s Lemmy doing vox on this version. According to Starfarer (starfarer.net/gigs1972.html) Calvert wasn&#039;t at this gig.

Tracks: Silver Machine and Welcome to the Future.
